Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be one dashing man,\Nbut to think he had such habits...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ozu is in the same year I am. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because he hates vegetables\Nand only eats instant food,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he has an exceedingly ghastly face{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that looks like it came from\Nthe dark side of the moon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He picks on the weak and sucks\Nup to the strong. He's lazy and a devil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My soul would have surely\Nstayed unblemished had I not met him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how did you get a duplicate key?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've earned Jougasaki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s trust, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You back-stabbing bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you move anything, make sure to\Nput it back exactly where you found it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one serious clean freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean freak?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's why his girlfriend is\Nlike that instead of flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boor such as yourself whose mind is\Nfilled with sex probably couldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a form of extremely sophisticated love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:32.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tatami Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I was a brand-spanking new freshman\Nuniversity student and before my eyes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were held out innumerable circle fliers\Nfar surpassing my personal information intake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In each and every one of them I could\Nsee a door to that rose-colored campus life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the one I chose was... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There I was sure lay my\Nfuture of pure, sparkling gold.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My new cinema paradise with the raven-haired\Nmaidens dancing on the silver screen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I decided to join that day\Nin order to make 100 friends,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}led astray by the naive words of\N"Let's have fun making movies together."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was truly an idiot beyond all redemption.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:39.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sincerity vs. Authority
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the movie circle\N"Misogi" which I joined that day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was under authoritarian rule\Nby the president, Jougasaki-senpai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take 12, ready... Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Teacher and Student Go to War
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:57.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Jougasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just not right yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout this! After the\Nbreak, let me do another take.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit... To hell with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While I was annoyed with\NJougasaki-senpai's meaningless productions,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was then that an ominous man\Nstood beside me with a face of ill portent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from the dark side\Nof the moon? Or perhaps an E.T.?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say some pretty mean things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry,\NI am your compatriot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was my first contact with Ozu,\Nas well as worst contact.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he does is parrot what he's\Nread in how-to-make-movies books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it's Godard\Nand Truffaut and the like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the all-time best\Nis actually that Titanic guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to have a guy whose head\Nis only filled with boobs run the movie circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Movies must definitely not be allowed\Nto be poisoned by commercialism!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us a movie circle the way it\Nshould be, with your own two hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the purpose of raising the beacon\Nof mutiny against Jougasaki-senpai's faction,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I started filming my own personal movies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:32.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Approach
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My first work: after the war in the Pacific,\Ntwo men continue a battle of historic pranks,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}exhausting the limits of\Nintelligence and physical strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A movie of overflowing war and violence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, it was ignored, and the only person\Nin the theater that laughed was Akashi-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My second work: a sentimental movie\Nabout a man wavering between three women,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}patterned after King Lear. It received a storm\Nof vilification from the women's camp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my third work: a man trapped in\Na never-ending maze of 4.5 tatami rooms{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his attempts to escape from it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was DOA after people said "I've seen\Nthis premise before somewhere..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akashi-san was the only one\Nwho gave me useful criticism.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yojou-han
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:04.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The End
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was odd was that I couldn't help\Nbut think that the more effort I put in,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the more Jougasaki-senpai's\Ncharisma seemed to rise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next work shall\Nbe Alexander the Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will surely be a super grade-A piece of\Nentertainment, the culmination of our work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, everyone... Will you follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ablution!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I think back on it now, I was used\Nas leverage to increase his charismatic appeal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Undaunted by Jougasaki-senpai, we attempted\Nto announce a new romance film we were shooting,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but his faction was unanimously against it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The enemy's first line\Nof attack was Aijima-senpai,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jougasaki-senpai's right-hand man,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who always picked on us annoyingly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using acrobatic tricks of the\Nfilming schedule and petty things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}like turning off the electricity, hiding\Nthe key etc... He shut us out from the studio.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To even borrow the editing equipment\Nfelt like having to near prostrate ourselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end no one would deal with me,\Nand I was shut out of the movie circle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he be so celebrated while\Nwe have to resign ourselves to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... The public is finicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they will always recognize\Na film that's true to itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when will that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want recognition now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite selfish, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're really so motivated, why do you have\Nsuch a down-in-the-dumps look on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you I've wasted\Nmy perfectly lovely college life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I think you're also to blame for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it doesn't matter which path you take,\Nyou'll keep ending up right where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we had this conversation before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.\NIt's déjà vu, just déjà vu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, once I met you I put all\Nmy efforts into making you no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you haunt me so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the way I show my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're connected by the \Nblack thread of fate, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Japan Trench
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, here. This is Jougasaki-{\i1}senpai{\i0}'s transcript.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a great face, but\Nwhat's inside his head is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in his eighth year?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And moreover, his grades\Nare dangerously low!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't underestimate\Nmy information-gathering network.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to escape from this sad reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his heart has been more and more captured\Nby the boobs of his female circle members.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also the reason behind\Nthat last infamous swimsuit audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He filmed them in the swimsuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no exhibitionism\Nin the actual film.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's exactly\Nwhat made it so infamous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an aside, here are\Nthe marks from the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows the breasts' shape,\Nangle, size, and separation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely mixed up his\Nprivate fetish with his public behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Boob, boob, boob, boob...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then he's just a boob dictator!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. In short,\Nhe's nothing but a boob junkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a boob drunkard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu! I have an idea.\NWill you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to leave the circle anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So at least I want to bring down heavenly\Njudgment on Jougasaki-{\i1}senpai {\i0}before the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, that's not very calm of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll follow you\Nwherever you go, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And thus I was driven to action\Nby my righteous indignation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now is the time to throw\Ncold water on the people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or to put it simply, I decided to film an\Nexposé documentary on Jougasaki-senpai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to save the underclassmen charmed\Nby Jougasaki-senpai's meager charisma,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I decided to willingly take on\Nthis villainous role myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still soft-balling it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The man that Ozu had\Nbrought in as an adviser{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}seemed to have known\NJougasaki-senpai for a long time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Ozu schemed to\Nhis fullest extent to shoot{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}yet more and more libelous\Nscenes of his discordant private life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ozu was like a kid in a candy factory,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}continuously manipulating\Nthe film to deviate from reality,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the exposé film became nothing\Nmore than a personal attack film.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should try going this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Documentaries are deliberate, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, let's keep going on this, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's sure looking like this will be\Nan epoch-making work, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and by the way, please\Nonly credit yourself, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I left the editing room and\Nwalked aimlessly around Kiyamachi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}under the overhang of someone's house{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was caught by an old woman who\Nemitted a suspiciously ghoulish aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This unplaceable aura was\Npersuasive, and thinking logically,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there was no way that the fortune-telling{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}of a creature who emits such an\Naura could be anything but spot on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is a face of extreme\Nimpatience... You are unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that you are not in a\Nsituation that you believe suits you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can sense your fiercely earnest talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly I did tip my hat to\Nthe old woman's keen insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I sense there is an\Nopportunity you can't let pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As in an excellent chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know what it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This opportunity is always\Ndangling in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must grab this\Nopportunity and act on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling I've heard this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will walk this life\Nas now, ever unchanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 2000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you raise your prices?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the viewer think is best?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spreading around emotions that can move\Na large number of viewers is basic etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hollywood system\Nis the best in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad your proposal wasn't accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But movies are things everyone should see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you make things\Nyou like that make no sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you want to show them to other people,\Nat least keep a minimum of etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are you wasting\Nthe viewer's precious time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's basically like showing you masturbating\Nto other people! I couldn't stand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck, my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, he's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director! I've been searching for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so my determination to push forward{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and create a libelous film against\NJougasaki-senpai was renewed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Below my feet ran the Takase River,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just as shallow as all the mass-produced\Nindependent films Jougasaki-senpai ever made.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Afterwards I returned to the editing room,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and on the morning of the fourth day,\Nafter three days of editing without sleep,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally completed the worthless\Ndocumentary which one could say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was the culmination of my two prior years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing a screening. Please come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your chance is during the staff\Nintroductions before they show the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head to the projector room then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This movie was created by\Nthe hard work of everyone in Misogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really put our all into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that you will all enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we start,\Nlet me introduce the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ozu-{\i1}kun{\i0}, who helped\Nwith the sound recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing both sides are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And next we have Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}, who was\Nin charge of the 3D and visual effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I met Akashi-san during Jougasaki-senpai's\Nshoot at Mt. Yoshida the previous year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was one year younger than me\Nand in the engineering department,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she was hired on as\Nstaff for her technical skills.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always meticulous, with\Nnever an equipment mishap,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she gained the trust of the other staff,\Nbut as she was not one to mince words,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it seemed there was a distance\Nbetween her and the people in her class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With her sharp tongue she held\Nher own against Jougasaki-senpai,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and although he took an interest in her\Nchilly, intelligent demeanor (and her boobs),{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he never spoke with her, fearful his\Ncharismatic flair would be damaged.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}, you sure are fair-skinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, fair-skinned?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of people with fairer skin\Nthan me, so on what basis do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With such a resolute denial\Nand then cross-examination,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}no man ever dared\Nspeak with her after that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:15:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sent off a fiery cheer of "Akashi-san, you just\Nkeep doing things your own way!" in my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You created another idiotic movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for making you\Nwatch such a worthless film.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was definitely worthless,\Nbut I didn't hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we will start the film!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy it to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Alexander
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, maybe we should call it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bring myself to\Ndo it with Akashi-{\i1}san {\i0}here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? What happened\Nto your pride as a filmmaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,\Nyou're on their crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having fun, Alexander?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink will not clear my mind, Ptolemaeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:15:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm definitely a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut off the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, didn't he realize this was recording?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a camera on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those his?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do? I barely\Nhave enough money to eat, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me... A wall of boobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this non-fiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so then... wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie, this is all a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop the film!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop it, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're very pretty again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go to sleep?\NLet's change your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? We'll smoke him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really fast at running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't like it when\Nthings get complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to stop\Nhanging out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After forcing me to do all that,\Nthat's quite a thing for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, someone is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You created another idiotic movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't stop the screening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The viewers found it interesting, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Jougasaki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\Nfaction is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll probably be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad the people\Nwatching had a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he'd call entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I preferred your earlier films.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one was of questionable character.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever... It was a hit-and-run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you haven't kept your promise yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, hurry up and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! Now, Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}, fare thee well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not be fooled by Jougasaki's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I seriously look like such a fool to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so I left behind the site of my unproductive,\Nagonizing struggle over the past two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I returned to the boarding house,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone had sloppily eaten the Castella\Nthat Ozu had brought me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason I was tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like my reason had\Ncrumbled to pieces like that Castella.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking my next film\Nwould be about true love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A true love film?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A love romance where\Ntwo people tied by fate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would overcome their positions,\Nages, and even sexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like it's going to\Nturn into something weird again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go, Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I squished it... I s-squished it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. I am not fond of moths.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are called Mochiguman, and they\Ncome in sets of five, but I have lost one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not! As this Earth is round,\Nyou are sure to meet once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or if you'd like,\NI'll help you search for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather you make that movie a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise? So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This opportunity is always\Ndangling in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I didn't hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't get carried away with your dreams.\NThat's what I kept telling myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had no confidence I could comprehend\Na woman who could understand my selfish movies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so I tried watching\Nmy latest, unfinished film.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't shake off the feeling of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for choosing the movie circle "Misogi"\Nin front of that fateful clock tower.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I had joined some other circle, like\Nfor instance the human flight circle "Birdman,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would have surely spent\Nquite a different two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will always haunt me so, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way I show my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
